  8:{name:'Hope',prompt:'The Syndicate collapses and communities inherit the ruins of an interstellar civilization. Faith, science, and magic begin to converge again as people rebuild deliberately rather than simply restoring what failed. Hope is practical work: teaching, repairing, growing, organizing, exploring, and defending fragile futures from the systems that still want to return.',roles:['teacher','engineer','gardener','mystic','organizer','artist','navigator','repairer','healer','historian','builder','mediator','farmer','signal keeper'],phrases:['Find yourself here','What will you become','Build what comes next','Choose your becoming','Become part of the future','Who will you help'],path:['Builder','The future is not waiting to be discovered, waiting for someone to show up with tools.','8 regions · 34 communes · 109 unfinished plans']}
